{"word":"G120 - ἀθυμέω - athyméō - ath-oo-meh'-o - Be dismayed","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀθυμέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>athyméō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>ath-oo-meh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Be dismayed"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - திடனற்றுப் போ"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to be disheartened, dispirited, broken in spirit"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From a compound of <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and <a href=\"#/G2372 - θυμός - thymós - thoo-mos'/2372\">G2372</a>; to <i>be spiritless</i>, that is, <i>disheartened:</i> - be dismayed."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"}]}